sql:
SELECT name
FROM renters
WHERE credit_score > 650;

external_knowledge:
- Comprehensive details include property ID, street address, city, state, zip, property type, number of bedrooms and bathrooms, square footage, year built, property status, average rental price, review count, and total maintenance cost; 
- Average rental price is the mean of all rental prices for properties of the same type; 
- Lease counts represent the number of active leases for a property; 
- The earliest lease start date and the latest lease end date represent the start and end dates of the earliest and the latest lease, respectively, for each property; 
- Total payments represent the sum of all payments made for a property; 
- Payment counts represent the number of payments made for a property.
